lin, particularly in patients with advanced age and/or renal impairment.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/113115/', '', 'Liraglutide, Lixisenatide', 'Capreomycin, Pyrazinamide, Rifamycin, Bedaquiline, Rifapentine, Streptomycin, Trimethoprim, Rifampicin, Cycloserine, Rifabutin, Ethambutol, More', 1767369485);
